  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcade Boss Simulator is an arcade store simulation where you profit from arcade machines and collect those coins to expand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss Around:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Organize your store the way you want , provide your customers with a wide selection to increase profits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3725770/extras/5cf170de57441dc36469a1a1505efea6.poster.avif?t=1758863651\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3725770/extras/5cf170de57441dc36469a1a1505efea6.webm?t=1758863651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3725770/extras/5cf170de57441dc36469a1a1505efea6.mp4?t=1758863651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss Prizes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy prizes to meet your customers requirements. Unlock new prize collections to display in your store or reward your customers with.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3725770/extras/086f0180e63e536ce0e350659f0a63c7.poster.avif?t=1758863651\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3725770/extras/086f0180e63e536ce0e350659f0a63c7.webm?t=1758863651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3725770/extras/086f0180e63e536ce0e350659f0a63c7.mp4?t=1758863651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss Decor:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add in fun decor to your store from a selection of neon signs and lights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3725770/extras/0e231516ef94a8d34732b6a0ee3af810.poster.avif?t=1758863651\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3725770/extras/0e231516ef94a8d34732b6a0ee3af810.webm?t=1758863651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3725770/extras/0e231516ef94a8d34732b6a0ee3af810.mp4?t=1758863651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss Expansion:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep expanding to add more machines to your store and keep up with the increasing customer demands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3725770/extras/d600820d870118a3f33aa9c5449e0975.poster.avif?t=1758863651\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3725770/extras/d600820d870118a3f33aa9c5449e0975.webm?t=1758863651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3725770/extras/d600820d870118a3f33aa9c5449e0975.mp4?t=1758863651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
